title: Signs You Are A Beta Male

slides.text: While there are obvious red flags such as being a man who is weak, inadequate, or a good listener, The Onion provides a helpful guide to signs  that you probably  are a beta male.

slides.header: Under 1'3"
slides.text: This height actually might suggest you are a dormouse.

slides.header: Inability To Sustain Erection For Longer Than 97 Years
slides.text: Alpha males stay hard long after their body has started moldering.

slides.header: Shopping For Food At A Grocery Store
slides.text: Alphas hunt or fuck their way to a meal.

slides.header: Lack Of Vestigial Tail
slides.text: Alphas are able to whip their opponents across the face, thus assuring sexual dominance.

slides.header: Cannot Do A Somersault For Mommy
slides.text: You would have impressed Mommy so much, but instead you fucking ruined her day, you cuck piece of shit.

slides.header: Your Penis Is 12 Inches Long
slides.text: While alphas have penises that are so long they touch the floor, betas have micropenises that can be as small as 12 inches flaccid.

slides.header: You Are A Human Being, Cursed With Knowing That You Are Imperfect And Understanding That You Could Be So Much More
slides.text: Unfortunately, perceiving the simultaneous splendid grace and humiliation of just being alive suggests you’re nothing more than a lowly beta.

slides.header: Enjoyed ‘Banshees Of Inisherin,’ But Didn’t Really ‘Get’ It
slides.text: The fact that you think you need to “get” something about Martin McDonagh’s tragicomic writing in order to appreciate his work suggests you’re an effete half-man.

slides.header: You Ask For Consent Before Taking Every Bite Of A Hamburger
slides.text: Alphas don’t even wait for the animal to die before sinking their teeth in.

slides.header: Feet Don’t Twist Off And Detach
slides.text: Should be springs under there that you have to replace every two years.

slides.header: Pink, Rotund, And Able To Inhale Enemies To Save Planet Popstar
slides.text: If this is you, just give up. You’re never going to find a date.

slides.header: You Are No Muss No Fuss
slides.text: Alphas make a substantial amount of both muss and fuss.

slides.header: Only Having One Penis
slides.text: What are you, a girl?

slides.header: You Have Never Run With A Calf Upon Your Shoulders Every Day Until It Became A Full-Grown Ox, After Which You Butchered And Ate It In The Center Of The Olympic Stadium
slides.text: Milo of Croton would like a word.

slides.header: You Own Pajamas
slides.text: Alpha males work, live, and sleep in finely tailored suits.

slides.header: Criminal Background Check Reveals A Clean Record
slides.text: Ugh, humiliating.

slides.header: There Are Barely Any Women Dangling From Your Large Biceps
slides.text: An alpha would never step into public with fewer than 20.

slides.header: You Are Evan Davis Of 2269 Oak Ridge Drive, Seattle, Washington 98108
slides.text: You are worse than beta. You are scum.

slides.header: You Aren’t Currently Penetrating Anything
slides.text: Not a good look, cuck.

slides.header: You’re Still An Editorial Assistant After More Than 4 Years Toiling Away At ‘Dazzle’ Magazine
slides.text: An alpha male would have landed your dream gig of senior fashion editor years ago. Guess you’re not cut out for this business after all.

slides.header: Veins Do Not Bulge Out From Your Bald Head
slides.text: Worse yet, you cover them in dainty hairs.

slides.header: You Ejaculate Without Impregnating Anything
slides.text: Physiologically, the seed of a true alpha male could impregnate a pillow.

slides.header: Bards Don’t Write Ballads Lauding Your Tremendous Physical Strength
slides.text: Any alpha male knows that by the time you’re 30, there should be a whole band of lute players following you from town to town in order to record your feats.

slides.header: Stepping Out Of The Shower Onto A Roller Skate That Propels You Toward The Stairs And Bounces Down Each Step Before You Head Straight Out The Door With Nothing But A Towel On
slides.text: An alpha would never conceal his manhood with a towel.

slides.header: Have Been Stuck In A Well For 20 Years
slides.text: No matter how much betas scream and scream, they will never emerge from the well.

slides.header: You Do Not Mate With The Other Elephants
slides.text: Oof, nothing says “solitary non-breeding male” more than failing to produce any calves.

slides.header: Harem Keeps Making Excuses Why They Can’t Hang Out Tonight
slides.text: Is your harem really holding a concubines-only movie marathon night, or are you just low T?

slides.header: Eating With Your Mouth
slides.text: If you don’t know, you don’t know. It’s not something we can teach.

slides.header: Birds Do Not Fear You
slides.text: They’re very perceptive to the varying degrees of manliness.
